{
  "stem": "3952.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What I worked, I worked first at a certain firma that was called HUTA, HUTA, H-U-T-T-A, a German firm.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were-- they were cutting trees, cleaning trees from the forest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we were cutting these huge trees.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "A brother of my very close friend of mine was killed by a tree.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "A tree fell and he ran the wrong side, and he got killed by a tree in that camp, at the beginning in Wolfsberg.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so you would have to be very careful, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They taught you how to cut the trees.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then you would peel off the trees.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then you would send the trees down the mountain, you know, those logs, those huge ones.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then I worked later for a firma called Dubiner who would build houses, houses for the Italian prisoners.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "When Badoglio took over Italy and Mussolini was ran away, so the Italians were not working with the Germans hand in hand.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So they took their armament and they kept them as prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So we build their houses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then, Later, I worked at the small firm called Firma Angrick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were only three Jewish boys and there were two-- two Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they taught us how to make the central heating for those buildings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And these work there was pretty good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The whole-- the life in Wolfsberg for the nine months that we were there was considerably good, meaning by good was that you had for three men a bread.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Later a little, you got four men a bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And at the end, you got 18 men a bread, the same loaf of bread divided into 18, so you got a cubicle of bread.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But at the beginning, we got three men a bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
